# Web3Forms access key used by the "Book Demo" modal to email submissions
# to hello@shiksit.com. Get a free key at https://web3forms.com by
# registering with hello@shiksit.com — the key is tied to that inbox.
PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=

# Optional spam protection for the "Book Demo" form. Leave blank to skip —
# the form works fine without it (just relies on the honeypot field).
# To enable:
#   1. Get a free site key + secret key at https://www.hcaptcha.com
#   2. Paste the SITE key below.
#   3. Paste the SECRET key into your Web3Forms dashboard
#      (Form settings → Spam Protection → hCaptcha) so Web3Forms can verify
#      it server-side — the secret key never goes in this repo.
PUBLIC_HCAPTCHA_SITE_KEY=
